{"tid":700481,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家會屌邊個？","createTime":"2018-06-13T11:14:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T11:27:17.000Z","uid":42252,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1c5c32b9424122c5ad621d777294dcfbe75d5d44","tid":700481,"uid":42252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T11:14:35.000Z","msg":"長話短說 打工仔人人騎牛搵馬 有咩錯<br />\n我係現公司做經理 原本過兩日要帶班細既出trip傾大生意<br />\n但咁岩琴日新公司有offer 我當然答應啦<br />\n但呢行好窄 好易比人知 咁當然比現公司都好快知道啦 搞到老闆嬲嬲地 本身我都諗住做埋呢個月 傾成埋份大生意當多謝舊老闆就走人 <br />\n但點知轉個頭老闆話要炒我 仲要即時 咁我而家唯有去新公司準備下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 轉工啫犯法咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌舊公司好小器"},{"pid":"400393ff1c6b11fe53b8329fba53d6262f93dad7","tid":700481,"uid":139468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T11:22:48.000Z","msg":"覺得轉工無問題又想屌舊公司可以點投？"},{"pid":"5df35b3b546434a611b46ae7e17ea877deb495fb","tid":700481,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T11:23:50.000Z","msg":"投你老母<br />\n負皮上一頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c24e146244906b82167a4c83e3ed53a8ee37955","tid":700481,"uid":42252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"400393ff1c6b11fe53b8329fba53d6262f93dad7","tid":700481,"uid":139468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T11:22:48.000Z","msg":"覺得轉工無問題又想屌舊公司可以點投？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T11:27:17.000Z","msg":"個題開得唔好 應該係大家點睇？"}]}